net.fathomsoft.nova.tree

Class ValueNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.fathomsoft.nova.tree.TreeNode
      • net.fathomsoft.nova.tree.ValueNode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BinaryOperatorNode, ExternalTypeNode, IdentifierNode, LiteralNode, OperatorNode, PriorityNode, ReturnNode, UnaryOperatorNode

    public class ValueNode
extends TreeNode
    TreeNode extension that represents something that returns a value. For the rules on what can and cannot be an value node, refer to setType(java.lang.String)
    Since:

 FILE varName;
